PHILOSOPHY:

This license reflects the belief that AI and computer vision technology should 
empower humanity while respecting fundamental human rights, privacy, and dignity. 
We encourage responsible innovation that benefits society while preventing harmful 
applications that could undermine democratic values or human welfare.

Use this technology to build a better world, not to control or harm it. 